of motion within the framework of Hamiltonian mechanics.\nAnother result of the paper is the extension of the solution technique to more\ngeneral drag laws, such as general power laws or power laws with an additional\nlinear contribution. Furthermore, generalization to variable velocity of the\nsurrounding fluid is addressed by considering a linear velocity profile for\nwhich a solution is provided as well. Throughout, the results obtained are\nillustrated by numerical examples.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 6 May 2013 19:32:10 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 15 May 2013 19:42:01 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Tue, 11 Jun 2013 19:43:39 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Wed, 12 Jun 2013 19:39:39 GMT"},{"version":"v5","created":"Thu, 11 Sep 2014 23:28:23 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-23"}
