 pairs (Z,H) in X\nwhere H is a member of the linear system |L| and Z is a 1-dimensional subscheme\nof H. The associated sheaf is the ideal sheaf of Z in H, pushed forward to X\nand considered as a certain Joyce-Song pair in the derived category of X. We\nexpress these invariants in terms of the MNOP invariants of X.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 6 May 2013 21:22:00 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 8 May 2013 13:50:51 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Tue, 3 Sep 2013 00:32:31 GMT"}],"update_date":"2013-09-04"}
