ws of rotating BECs such as the dynamics of condensate\nwidth, angular momentum expectation and center-of-mass, and to investigate\nnumerically the dynamics and interaction of quantized vortex lattices in\nrotating BECs without/with the long-range dipole-dipole interaction.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 7 May 2013 01:47:39 GMT"}],"update_date":"2013-11-21"}
