e directly affected by\nstellar encounters, but also planets close to the star which can disappear long\nafter a stellar encounter has perturbed the planetary system.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 7 May 2013 05:45:57 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-15"}
